{"tid":1005074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社又贏】香港前途研究計劃衝出國際","createTime":"2019-02-02T03:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T10:51:17.000Z","uid":138409,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ffaadfdc2880f59669c9c2578feeb71f39955d","tid":1005074,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sk6AoQN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsk6AoQN.jpg&h=bf8ac867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中方近年聲稱《中英聯合聲明》已是歷史文件，不具任何現實意義，言論不但惹來政界譁然，同時亦引起英國政界關注。英國國會下議院外交事務委員會日前展開有關香港事務的聽證會，談到過去一年言論自由收緊、行政當局利用《社團條例》打擊政治團體等問題。<br />\n<br />\n席間，80年代中英談判的檔案紀錄亦成為聽證會重點。在聽證會快將結束之際，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國研究學者魏簡教授（Sebastian Veg）突然打插發言，要求英國政府盡快解封有關中英談判的檔案，並指英國欠香港人有關當時的提出的承諾、談判過程的確實資訊。</span><br />\n<br />\n在聽證會後，魏簡教授聯絡 黃之鋒 Joshua Wong 和 香港前途研究計劃 Decoding Hong Kong's History，要求提供有關封存檔案的資訊。<span style=\"color: gold;\">我們整理了1000多份涉及中英談判的英國檔案名單之餘，更向魏簡教授提及有一大批最高級別的「Migrated Archives」（註），現在存放在英國外交部，開放無期，並透過魏簡教授要求英方盡快公開相關檔案。<br />\n</span><br />\n這些檔案大多以「中國因素」，被封存至2049年才可公開，令香港人無法得悉這段被封存的歷史。正如魏簡教授所言，香港人有權得知中英兩方當年各自許下什麼承諾，而英國作為監察《中英聯合聲明》落實狀況的一方，亦有責任公開所有與主權移交相關的檔案紀錄，還香港人知情權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港前途研究計劃在未來一年亦會繼續「追數」，透過《資訊自由法》要求相關部門盡快解封1000份香港檔案。</span>想知道外交事務委員會討論過什麼議題，大家可以到以下Twitter 連結看看會議內容：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2CYKdLr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2CYKdLr&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=a5b5f7c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2CYKdLr</a><br />\n<br />\n註：香港前途研究計劃 - 英國外交部 秘密扣起港英政府檔案 公開時間表一拖再拖<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2D2Dekz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2D2Dekz&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=f6a41292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2D2Dekz</a>"},{"pid":"a4a243f3befdfe84f708aad6269796dc4f4986a4","tid":1005074,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"█ 解密過去🔓重掌未來 █<br />\n💰捐款支持：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IVW56L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IVW56L&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=cb375199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IVW56L</a><br />\n📖研究成果：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@decodinghkshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40decodinghkshistory&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=4bce16a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@decodinghkshistory</a><br />\n🗂計劃詳情：<a href=\"https://researchforfuture.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresearchforfuture.hk&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=45d143f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://researchforfuture.hk</a><br />\n📧聯絡 #香港前途研究計劃： <a href=\"http://m.me/decodinghkhistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fdecodinghkhistory&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=a9582f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.me/decodinghkhistory</a>"},{"pid":"d85e79436f7cc8ffeda5d4e7ee71ce7a2d224cbf","tid":1005074,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2388d5b4664fd7687a3cbc064259d2653edef21e","tid":1005074,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/photos/a.812247002262598/1192926537527974/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fphotos%2Fa.812247002262598%2F1192926537527974%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2XwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=49bb1158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/photos/a.812247002262598/1192926537527974/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"8c89e9f11aefbfc8dc5c43f2dfdc59dc267ad879","tid":1005074,"u